SetupWizard_FirstPage_Title.en_US: Welcome to the Tears of the Kingdom Mod Manager!

SetupWizard_FirstPage_Content.en_US:
This setup wizard will guide you through setting up TKMM to work with your computer.

Click the info button (i) in the bottom left at any time to get more information.

SetupWizard_Popup_InvalidEmulatorSelecti.en_US: Please choose one of the options before proceeding.

SetupWizard_EmulatorSelection_Title.en_US: How are you playing Tears of the Kingdom?

SetupWizard_RyujinxSetup_Content.en_US: Make sure you have the prod and title keys configured and have "The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom" installed with at least one update.

SetupWizard_MissingKeys_Content.en_US: The production keys (prod.keys) and/or title keys (title.keys) are missing, please reboot to Hekate and inject the latest version of the Lockpick_RCM payload to dump them.

SetupWizard_MissingDump_Content.en_US:
TKMM was unable to find or decrypt your game dump.

Either the game is missing, or the provided keys were insufficient to access its content.

To dump your keys, please reboot to Hekate and inject the latest version of the Lockpick_RCM payload.

If you are using a cartridge or your game or game update is installed to internal memory, please dump it using NxDumpTool.

SetupWizard_GameDumpConfigPage_InvalidCo.en_US: The provided configuration is incomplete or invalid, please review your configuration.

SetupWizard_GameDumpConfigPage_SdCardFol.en_US: * If the base game or update is missing from your SD card, add the missing files in the fields below.

SetupWizard_NxDumpConfigPage_Help.en_US:
If you have reached this page, the game was either not installed on your SD card, or your keys were not able to decrypt it.

If your game is a cartridge, you can dump it as a split XCI using nxdumptool.

Error_IncompleteRomConfig.en_US: Failed to retrieve TotK rom. Please review your TotK configuration.
